SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES

New Invocable Actions for Einstein Bots

Use the new invocable actions and changed metadata type for Einstein Bots. To use these actions and values, you must enable Lightning Knowledge.

Search for knowledge articles based on data category and data category groups 
Use the new searchKnowledgeArticles, getDataCategoryGroups, and getDataCategoryDetails actions.
Use the new searchKnowledgeArticles, getDataCategoryGroups, and getDataCategoryDetails values in the existing actionType field.
